Φ(PsychicScience) = σ(perception|anomalous) ∘ ρ(consciousness|connection) ∘ λ(evidence|challenge) ∘ β(paradigm|expansion) ∘ δγ(empirical|embodied) ∘ μ(methodology|rigor) + ε | :paradigm_tension

; === Operator Breakdown ===

; σ — Air / Aerunik (0.86)
;   The dominant operator. Anomalous perception — awareness that extends beyond
;   conventional sensory channels. Telepathy (mind-to-mind communication),
;   clairvoyance (perception of distant events), precognition (perception of
;   future events). Aerunik governs the expansion of perceptual bandwidth into
;   domains that materialism declares impossible. The air element is most
;   congruent with phenomena that involve information transfer without physical
;   mediation.

; ρ — Water / Sentaria (0.79)
;   Consciousness as connective medium — the hypothesis that minds are not
;   isolated computational units but nodes in a nonlocal relational field.
;   Sentaria governs the deep connective substrate that psi research implies:
;   if telepathy is real, then consciousness has relational properties that
;   transcend spatial separation. Empathic resonance becomes literal rather
;   than metaphorical.

; λ — Fire / Jvalion (0.75)
;   The confrontational dimension. Statistical evidence (30.6% Ganzfeld hit
;   rate, 115 quintillion to one remote viewing odds) directly challenges
;   materialist orthodoxy. Jvalion fuels the evidential fire that forces
;   engagement — these numbers cannot be dismissed without engaging the
;   methodology. The fire is directed at philosophical bias, not at individual
;   skeptics.

; β — Wood / Arboriel (0.72)
;   Paradigm expansion from strict materialism toward broader models of
;   consciousness. Arboriel nurtures the slow, organic growth of post-materialist
;   frameworks — theories that accommodate psi without abandoning empirical rigor.
;   This growth is generational, requiring patience as new models develop roots
;   strong enough to support institutional change.

; δγ — Earth / Humavita (0.68)
;   Laboratory protocols, replication studies, and embodied measurement.
;   Humavita grounds psi research in the material practices of experimental
;   science — shielded rooms, randomized targets, blinded judges, pre-registered
;   hypotheses. The relatively lower emphasis reflects the challenge of grounding
;   phenomena that may be inherently variable and context-sensitive.

; μ — Metal / Ferrosid (0.81)
;   Meta-analysis, statistical methodology, and peer review standards. Ferrosid
;   provides the structural backbone of the evidential case: rigorous statistical
;   methods (Bayesian analysis, effect-size estimation, file-drawer corrections)
;   that transform individual experiments into cumulative evidence. Without
;   metallic methodological discipline, anomalous claims cannot be distinguished
;   from noise.

; === Z-State ===
; Paradigm tension — evidence accumulates while institutional frameworks resist
; integration. The Z-state is not resolution but sustained tension: the data
; says one thing, the dominant paradigm says another, and the field exists in
; the gap between them.

; === Tendency ===
; σ → 0.86 — The system leans toward expanded perception (air). The phenomena
; themselves are perceptual extensions — they claim that awareness reaches further
; than materialist models allow. The dominant mode is receptive, not constructive.

# CE-STATE: multiscale
